snippet.title: Soulflow Trailer by Bluespy Studios | Next in Game #SteamNextFest
snippet.description:
SOULFLOW 👻

Get your deerstalker hats ready🕵️ !  

Use your deduction skills in order to survive. Wonder around in this unique artwork and try to survive. Try the most peculiar detective game in Steam Next Fest. 

❗️ Start your detective career by adding to your wishlist.
